{"tid":1722283,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"認清三罷嬴係邊輸係邊 唔好開心得咁早","createTime":"2019-11-15T00:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T17:32:18.000Z","uid":32731,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"15c9fcc2fdf6e50c783224fada55f1a5ff60c7ec","tid":1722283,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:41:05.000Z","msg":"首先和理非係無乜進步<br />\n只係圍魏救趙太突發主要影響到巴士安排<br />\n所以別無他法去搭鐵 心態上根本無唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於前線 人數有增加 而且開始係一啲之前無既區或邨做野 葵涌 青衣<br />\n有啲地方出地鐵都要巴士 所以除左行路外無其他方法<br />\n值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各大佔領主要幹道當然最成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次有進步 但都只限於前線<br />\n和理非根本爛泥扶唔上壁 亦有人提早返工<br />\n如果有做野塞錢鐵既和理非 辛苦你地<br />\n<br />\n巴士逐步恢復<br />\n所以鐵路站站停既時間都縮短緊<br />\n唔好以為成功得咁早"},{"pid":"667e4744481a8c4ad70b98e03910c59ba76add0d","tid":1722283,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:42:16.000Z","msg":"臥底便衣入唔到大學，派五毛大力屌把關守門既手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1722276\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1722276</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"70637c379ae79765a14c27e45dc4994b5cfe20bc","tid":1722283,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:42:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ec7f07fedeb47f823845618f1b5aa9a1545f27a","tid":1722283,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:42:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1823b595f78d40597760b2977f21d49a7b022e94","tid":1722283,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:43:20.000Z","msg":"唔係分化 但請認清事實"},{"pid":"3d6bce389aae8a52c27182e600f695ec2afe9e18","tid":1722283,"uid":32731,"like